  "Thailand": {
    "title": "Ode to Panang Curry - Khlong Si Suphap",
    "body": "Reminiscent Sun\t\t\tBurning\nBlessed tongue yearning\t\tfor joy\nFor mystifying\t\t\tflavor\nMy Helen Of Troy\t\t\tPanang Curry\nRed Sun Over The Nile\t\tbrings rain\nCovering white grain\t\twith grace\nKaffir lime leaves contain\t\tbeauty\nLike thorned roses’ base\t\tshunning lovers\nYet Love is Welcomed\t\twith love\nLike peace from white doves\tno man\nIs left not above\t\t\tit all\nTruly it fully spans\t\t\tall enjoyment\nGently cut chicken swimming\tin paste\nRed, like peppers based \t\tamong spice\nCrushed peanuts, embrace\theaven\n\nother reach such heights\tPanang Curry"
  },
